<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>Facebook</strong></p>
</div></div></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p>Link-Button zu <strong>Facebook</strong> anzeigen: Häkchen setzen.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>Twitter</strong></p>
</div></div></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
